I’m beyond grateful to everyone who watched the documentary for your love, support, and making this the #1 most watched doc in Amazon Prime history!!!

#ad I’ve been working with @goldbond and @ditrfoundation to spotlight diversity in the Stunt industry, and to help create a program for girls of color interested in pursuing a career in stunts. 
All applications for the Skin Champion Stunt Workshop have been reviewed, and I’m excited to share with you some of the applicants who were accepted! Congratulations, ladies! 💪🏾 #goldbondpartner 
Be a #SkinChampion. Learn how you can support Diamond In The Raw at www.diamondintheraw.org 
#diversityinstunts
